{
  "texts": [
    "4 Discussions of cases of with role of AI used to produce or to detect disinformation that we studied",
    "To illustrate the interplay between AI technologies, disinformation tactics, and societal impacts, we examine recent cases and developments across several categories of AI application.",
    "Below, we classify the main ways AI is used to produce disinformation and provide real-world examples of each, along with the harms they have caused.",
    "We also discuss how AI is being employed in counterdisinformation efforts.",
    "This classification underscores the dual nature of AI -as a tool for malign manipulation and as an instrument for defense."
  ]
}